<p><b>Sendmail</b> is a <a href="/wiki/Mail_transfer_agent" title="Mail transfer agent">mail transfer agent</a> (MTA) that supports many kinds of mail transfer and delivery including the overwhelmingly popular <a href="/wiki/SMTP" title="SMTP" class="mw-redirect">SMTP</a>.</p>
<p>A descendant of <i><a href="/wiki/Delivermail" title="Delivermail">delivermail</a></i> program written by <a href="/wiki/Eric_Allman" title="Eric Allman">Eric Allman</a>, Sendmail is a well-known project of the <a href="/wiki/Free_and_open_source_software" title="Free and open source software">free and open source software</a> and <a href="/wiki/Unix" title="Unix">Unix</a> communities, and is distributed both as <a href="/wiki/Free_software" title="Free software">free software</a> and <a href="/wiki/Proprietary_software" title="Proprietary software">proprietary software</a>.</p>
