<p><a name="History_of_vulnerabilities" id="History_of_vulnerabilities"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Sendmail&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6" title="Edit section: History of vulnerabilities">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">History of vulnerabilities</span></h3>
<p>Sendmail vulnerabilities in CERT advisories and alerts.</p>
<ul>
